00:02:47.820 --> 00:02:51.500
learn a foreign language... giving others the time of their lives...

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:53.620
...and have an incredible summer yourself?

00:02:53.720 --> 00:02:55.920
Than apply for a job with Vacansoleil!

00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:58.460
Take a look at www.campingjobs.co.uk for the vacancies.

